      enemyReactionText: Glup? (Soc el teu ninot de proves o que?)
      nextNodeId: 6
      requiredItem: {fileID: 0}
    - actionName: Plorar
      playerActionText: Plores, per arrepentiment pel que has fet...
      enemyReactionText: Glup...glup? (T'ha sabut greu... o sigui que potser no ets
        dolent del tot?)
      nextNodeId: 0
      requiredItem: {fileID: 0}
    - actionName: Espantar
      playerActionText: 'Mous la teva ma oberta de costat en costat, per intentar
